##<a id="ver"></a> v1.0.3

**Release Date:** June 26, 2019

Features included in this release:

* Credentials for Ops Manager and for PKS is stored now in Pivotal Platform (instead of Evolven in the previous version).
* Url for Ops and CF api are set on the tile setting page.
* Evolven agent will collect the applications content from Apps Manager only if they were modified since the last execution.
* New name given due to feature changes
* New version numbering to match name change

